description: Lists all of the policy generations requested in the last seven days.

parameters.name: principalArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the IAM entity (user or role) for which you are generating a policy. Use this with ListGeneratedPolicies to filter the results to only include results for a specific principal.

parameters.name: maxResults
parameters.description: The maximum number of results to return in the response.

parameters.name: nextToken
parameters.description: A token used for pagination of results returned.

nested_items.name: policyGenerations
nested_items.description: A PolicyGeneration object that contains details about the generated policy.

nested_items.name: jobId
nested_items.description: The JobId that is returned by the StartPolicyGeneration operation. The JobId can be used with GetGeneratedPolicy to retrieve the generated policies or used with CancelPolicyGeneration to cancel the policy generation request.

nested_items.name: principalArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the IAM entity (user or role) for which you are generating a policy.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the policy generation request.

nested_items.name: startedOn
nested_items.description: A timestamp of when the policy generation started.

nested_items.name: completedOn
nested_items.description: A timestamp of when the policy generation was completed.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token used for pagination of results returned.
